{"id":1284,"date":"2024-08-04T18:36:26","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T18:36:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1284"},"modified":"2024-08-29T23:32:32","modified_gmt":"2024-08-29T23:32:32","slug":"mission-081","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-081\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #081: Warmonger"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #081: Warmonger<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Great Desert, northeast cliffs &#8211; old man at cliff\u2019s edge<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Great Desert<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Fight 2000 Pokemon Battles<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/\">Lucarionite<\/a><\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>An old man in the Undying Lucario cult gives you an opportunity to join with a specific goal: fight 2,000 Pok\u00e9mon battles. After you do, he\u2019ll let you join the cult and give you the Lucarionite.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to Dehara City and take the east exit out of town into the Great Desert.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/081\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-great-desert-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"The Great Desert entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Great Desert entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From there, head northeast and follow the cliffs along until you see an old man along them with a mission for you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/081\/02-pokemon-unbound-an-invitation-to-join-a-cult.jpg\" alt=\"An invitation to join a cult \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>An invitation to join a cult<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The old man is a member of the Undying Lucario cult, and he wants you to fight 2000 Pok\u00e9mon battles to become one of them.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>Fighting 2000 Pok\u00e9mon battles just means \u2018entering 2000 encounters\u2019, whether they be with wild Pok\u00e9mon or trainers.<\/p>\n<p>Over the course of the main story, and if you\u2019ve been trying to catch as many Pok\u00e9mon as possible, you may have achieved at least half this number naturally.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> You don\u2019t need to defeat your opponent for it to count as a battle, so you can wander around long grass or surf and run from Pok\u00e9mon and it will still add to the total.\n<\/div>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/081\/03-pokemon-unbound-return-to-the-old-man.jpg\" alt=\"Return to the old man \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Return to the old man<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Once you\u2019ve achieved the 2000-battle feat, return to the old man by the cliffs in the desert and he\u2019ll give you the <strong>Lucarionite<\/strong> as proof of your membership to the Undying Lucario.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1285,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1284","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1284","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1285"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1284"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1284"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}